name: Abundance of Echinothrix diadema and its substrate coverage in the Mombasa Marine National Park and Reserve (Kenya) in September-October 1997
description: Absolute abundance of Echinothrix diadema in the MombasaMarineNational Park and Reserve in September-October 1997, together withpercentages of substrate cover (seagrasses, algae, corals, sediment) at the different sampling locations. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Van Hout,T. (1998). Patterns of distribution of Echinothrix diadema (Echinodermata:Echinoidea) in the Mombasa Marine NationalPark and Reserve, Kenya.MSc Thesis. Vrije UniversiteitBrussel: Brussel. 71 pp.
